data.title: WFMU: The Flange & Frigate with DJ GeorgyGirl: Playlist from May 5, 2023
data.meta_description:
On today's Flange & Frigate Show with DJ GeorgyGirl, we've got a lovely, quiet, gentle show planned for you. Only joking! It's Black Sabbath icon Bill Ward's birthday today! We've got wall-to-wall Sabbath, Earth and Mythology so TURN IT UP!
Welcome to The Flange & Frigate - the UK's premier pub and social club, playing the finest in British psych, fey pop, mod, prog, and folk!
4 pm to 6 pm EST/9 pm to 11 pm GMT only on #sheenasjungleroom
#British #FeyPop #Lounge #Psych #Mod #WFMU #BlackSabbath #BillWard | Audio & playlist from May 5, 2023
